,"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Up to four images can be attached to a post. All images need to be a .jpg format."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Videos","level":2,"anchor":"Videos"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Similar to images, you can add videos to a post."}]},{"code":["let videoURL = URL(string: \"\/path\/to\/file\/beach.mp4\")","","do {","    let postResult = try await atProtoBluesky.createPostRecord(","        text: \"The waves on the beach are looking as beautiful as ever.\",","        embed: .video(video: Data(contentsOf: videoFileURL))","    )","","    print(postResult)","} catch {","    throw error","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Only one video can be added to a post, can be 100 MB or less, and must use the .mp4 format.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can upload up to 25 videos per day and the 25 videos canâ€™t exceed a total of 500 MB","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the day."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"aside","name":"Tip","style":"tip","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Bluesky allows you to upload GIFs the same way, as it considers it to be a special kind","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"of video.. The only difference with a GIF is the lack a player scrubber. The same restrictions"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with respect to videos apply to uploaded GIFs.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"text":"External Links","anchor":"External-Links","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can attach a website card to the post.","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["Task {","    print(\"Starting application...\")","","    do {","        let session = try await config.authenticate()","","        let externalLinkBuilder = ExternalLinkBuilder()","","        guard let link = URL(string: \"https